    <entry>
      <title>Hexo 框架(二) 美化自己的博客</title>
      <link href="/2021/07/28/Hexo-%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6-%E4%BA%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2021/07/28/Hexo-%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6-%E4%BA%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="选择-hexo-主题"><a href="#选择-hexo-主题" class="headerlink" title="选择 hexo 主题"></a>选择 hexo 主题</h2><p>1.修改站点配置文件</p><p>本主题选择的是 <a href="https://volantis.js.org/">volantis</a></p><blockquote><p>在 <code>blog/_config.yml</code> 文件中配置</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">theme:</span> <span class="string">volantis</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><blockquote><p>在终端中输入：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i hexo-theme-volantis</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h2 id="美化博客"><a href="#美化博客" class="headerlink" title="美化博客"></a>美化博客</h2><p>1.设置封面背景<br>    打开 <code>blog/node_module/hexo-theme-volantis/_config.yml</code> 或者 <code>blog/themes/volantis/_config.yml</code></p><ul><li>方法一<blockquote><p>修改</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cover:</span><br><span class="line">  background: 图片地址</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote></li><li>方法二<blockquote><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">backstretch:</span><br><span class="line">   enable: true (开启背景插件)</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">images:</span><br><span class="line">- 图片地址</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> ps: 推荐使用云服务器存储网站地址 (我使用的是腾讯云的数据万象)</p></blockquote></li></ul><p>2.自定义鼠标,自定义右键菜单</p><blockquote><p><a href="https://volantis.js.org/v4/theme-settings/">参考地址</a></p></blockquote><p>3.设置主页的右侧的个人图像</p><blockquote><p><a href="https://volantis.js.org/v4/theme-settings/">参考地址</a></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">:wq</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> hexo </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
